data.description: This unique country house with a large barn, located on a small acreage just outside city limits, yet minutes from Shawnee, is waiting for you to call it home! Upon entering the house, you will immediately notice the beautiful hardwood flooring throughout the upper main living areas. The kitchen has a nice layout with lots of storage space and a large pantry with an island that is open to the dining room looking down to the living room. With such a large open area you could imagine having two different living rooms. Walking a few steps down into the main living room, you will immediately notice the oversized space and the amount of light that flows in through the three large windows. The primary bedroom has a beautiful view of the acreage and a door to the back patio, a large walk-in closet and a primary bathroom with an updated shower. On the opposite side of the kitchen are bedrooms two and three that share a cute bathroom. With a large open concept floor plan and massive back porch deck, it’s a perfect house for entertaining friends and family. The property also boasts a large vintage red barn, with a half bathroom and chicken coop ready for your livestock and hobbies. The property is partially fenced with a storm shelter next to the garage. Don’t miss out on this unique piece of real estate located in North Rock Creek School District and minutes from restaurants and shopping!
